<bibRefCitation id="EFBC26F7F77FB13EB518FEB432FA42CB" author="Dickinson, E. C. &amp; Remsen, J. V." pageId="10" pageNumber="531" refId="ref28348" refString="Dickinson, E. C. &amp; Remsen, J. V. (2013) The Howard and Moore Complete Checklist of the Birds of the World. 4 th Edition. Vol. 1. Non-passerines. Aves Press, Eastbourne, 461 pp." type="book" year="2013">Dickinson &amp; Remsen 2013: 294</bibRefCitation>
